{"tid":1137594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[金仔又想點?] 南韓軍方指北韓早上試射短程飛行物","createTime":"2019-05-04T02:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T05:03:09.000Z","uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3bfcd023e6f92a16422b6181dcb6170df76ebb","tid":1137594,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南韓軍方指，北韓早上試射幾枚短程飛行物。<br />\n<br />\n南韓聯合參謀本部公布，北韓在當地時間早上9時6分，從江原道元山地區虎島半島一帶，向東發射幾枚短程飛行物，飛行距離為70至200公里。<br />\n<br />\n軍方原本指，北韓是試射短程導彈，但後來改變說法，指是短程飛行物，韓美兩國正分析情況。<br />\n<br />\n平壤對上一次試射導彈是在2017年11月，當時射試火星-15型新型洲際彈道導彈。<br />\n<br />\n今次是二月河內舉行的美朝峰會破局後，北韓第二次測試武器。北韓上月宣稱成功試射一種新型戰術制導武器，領袖金正恩亦有到場監察並指導。<br />\n<br />\n而在昨日，北韓多間媒體同時在報道中，指摘駐南韓美軍部署薩德反導彈系統並進行演習，是公然針對北韓的威脅恐嚇。又要求南韓政府知進退、懂分寸，警告盲從美國的敵對行為將帶來不良後果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=346757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346757&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW95NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=57a80032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346757&h=5ccf2134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=346757</a>"},{"pid":"d6f452e9db930ec1cfbc8a7c8ab8d799512b5589","tid":1137594,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"早洩"},{"pid":"4debdf8707526014b435b31f9cbbfdab1425294c","tid":1137594,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"trump同北韓傾條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67ff8b579995edb6dd59c90288aa170466cb5df","tid":1137594,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"短程飛行物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家興軍事正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}